<html lang='en'>

  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Email Verification</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9; margin: 0; padding: 0; color: #333; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 30px auto; padding: 30px;
      background-color: #fff; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,
      0, 0, 0.1); } .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; } .header
      img { width: 150px; margin-bottom: 20px; } .content { text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px; } .content p { font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 20px; } .otp { background-color: #4CAF50; color: #fff;
      padding: 15px 30px; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 20px; display:
      inline-block; margin-bottom: 30px; } .note { font-size: 14px; color: #666;
      line-height: 1.6; } .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 14px; color: #666; border-top: 1px solid #ccc; padding-top:
      20px; }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <img
          src='https://sendpulse.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/verification-service-cover-1-1110x420.png'
          alt='E-commerce Image'
        />
      </div>
      <div class='content'>
        <p>Welcome to our E-commerce Platform!</p>
        <p>Please use the following One-Time Password (OTP) to complete your
          email verification:</p>
        <div class='otp'>{{otp}}</div>
        <p class='note'>This OTP is valid for a limited time and can only be
          used once.</p>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        <p>Please click the following link to verify your OTP:
          <a href='{{verifyLink}}'>Verify OTP</a></p>
        If you didn't sign up on our e-commerce, you can safely ignore this
        email.<br />
